highlights.text: “意外現場” by Yan Ting is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hong Kong, up 90 spots at #76.
“反對無效” by MC 張天賦 has been on Top Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 1573 days straight.
MC 張天賦 has the most spots on Top Songs Hong Kong. “東邪” is the highest at #20.
“JANE DOE” by Kenshi Yonezu and Hikaru Utada is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hong Kong at #46.
